      • craft

        boolean craft(java.util.function.Function<org.cyclops.commoncapabilities.api.ingredient.IngredientComponent<?,?>,org.cyclops.integrateddynamics.api.part.PartPos> targetGetter,

        Start a crafting process with the given ingredients.
        Parameters:
        targetGetter - A function to get the target position.
        ingredients - The ingredients to insert.
        resultsSink - A sink where the ingredients can optionally be inserted into. This should only be used if the processor does not have an internal storage.
        simulate - If insertion should be simulated.
        Returns:
        If all instances could be inserted.
